Victoria Macaulay (ka amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 7 n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1990) bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ bọọlụ bọọlụ na Naijiria maka otu ụmụ nwanyị Naịjirịa ma bụrụ onye nweere onwe ya na Women's National Basketball Association (WNBA) na
Na 2015 na 2019 ọ gbara bọọlụ na Chicago Sky na Women's National Basketball Association
N'oge ọ nọ n'akụkụ Nice nke France, ọ nwetara akara 15.8, 8.6 rebounds na 0.8 rebounds.

A kpọrọ Macaulay ma nọchite anya Naịjirịa na 2019 FIBA Women's AfroBasket ebe ndị otu ahụ meriri ọla edo na-eme ka onye nnọchi anya ya na Dakar. O nwetara akara 6.4, 3.4 rebounds na 1.2 na-enyere aka n'oge asọmpi ahụ na Dakar. O sonyekwara na 2020 FIBA Women's Olympic Qualifying Tournaments na Belgrade
